name: Blue Moose Tees
tag_list: custom-t-shirts, custom-embroidery, t-shirts, apparel, polo, screen-print, embroidery
overview:
Blue Moose Tees, the newest member of the B&E Industries family, was created to serve startups, small businesses, and schools spirit gear and apparel needs. These three customer groups are served by Blue Moose Tee’s dependable and low cost solution for custom apparel. For almost 20 years, B&E through its divisions, Sports Promotion Network, Spirit Stop, Primetime Advertising and Athletic Sports Group, have produced spirit items for over 9,000 customers annually across the United States making B&E one of the oldest and largest spirit item providers printing more than 5 million spirit and apparel products in 2007 alone!

Blue Moose Tees may be a new brand, but its not three guys in a garage printing shirts or a web site selling for a third party.

The Moose lives in an 80,000 sq. ft. state of the art production facility with customer service representatives, art staff, print staff and inventory brought together under one roof to serve their customer’s apparel needs.

At B&E, Blue Moose Tees’ parent Company, there are 300 employees taking great pride in guaranteeing customer’s satisfaction. Blue Moose offers a large selection of apparel, best in class graphic design and world class customer service at unbeatable prices.
